parameters.name: Input
parameters.description:
The priority of the job in the MPS queue to which the job is added.

*   Valid values: **1 to 10**. A value of 10 indicates the highest priority.
*   Default value: **6**.

parameters.name: PipelineId
parameters.description: The time when the job was created.

parameters.name: UserData
parameters.description: The information about the preset template analysis job that was submitted.
